* Editing
** Structured Editing
|----------------------------------------------------------+-----------|
| insert new heading at same hirachy after subsection      | C-RET     |
| promote / Demote                                         | M-h / l   |
| promote / Demote  subtree                                | M-S-h / l |
| move up / down                                          | M-j / k   |
| move up / down                                    single | M-S-j / k |
|----------------------------------------------------------+-----------|

** Advanced Editing
|----------------+-----|
| select element | vae |
| delete element | dae |
| select subtree | vaR |
| delete subtree | daR |
| yank subtree   | yaR |
|----------------+-----|
** Insert Snippets
|----------------+---------|
| Insert snippet | SPC-i-s |
|----------------+---------|

#+begin_example
insert current time: Mon Dec 11 18:56:56 2023
#+end_example

