* Getting Startet
Read the maunal with M-x "org-info"
** Motion
|--------------+--------------|
| move         | h / j / k /l |
| jump heading | gj / gk      |
| move text    | gh / gl      |
|--------------+--------------|

** Toggle
|---------------------+---------|
| org-toggle-heading: | SPC-m-h |
| org-toggle-item:    | SPC-m-i |
|---------------------+---------|
